BR_text.BRsummary: GME Blob Storage Backend missing config metadata
BR_text.BRdescription:
The configuration for the GME blob storage backend is missing configuration settings. This can cause problems when it is expected while generating configs in <denchmark-link:https://github.com/deepforge-dev/deepforge/pull/1270>#1270</denchmark-link>
  and related circumstances.
